column33: Total Time for WB = Total Read Time + Write Time for WB + (FCD_count*60nsec)
Total Time for WTNA = Total Read Time + Write Time for WTNA + (FCD_count*60nsec)
Total Time for WTA = Total Read Time + Write Time for WTA + (FCD_count*60nsec)
Total HIT Ratio = Read line HIT Ratio + Write Line HIT Ratio
Total MISS Ratio = (1 - Read line HIT Ratio) + (1 - Write line HIT Ratio)
Total Memory access time = (Total HIT Ratio * 1nsec) + (Total MISS Ratio *(60nsec+(BL-1)*17nsec))
